high_descs: Turn left for two steps, turn right and walk over to the stove.
Pick up the teakettle off the left front burner of the stove.
Turn around for four steps, turn left and walk over to the sink.
Put the teakettle in the sink, turn on the water and rinse the bottom of the teakettle, turn off the water and take the teakettle out of the sink.
Turn right for four steps, turn right and walk to the white trash bag and turn right to face the stove.
Put the teakettle on the table, close to the front edge with the handle pointed to the back.
anns.task_desc: Put a rinsed teakettle on the white table.

high_descs: Turn left then turn right and walk straight to the stove and face it
Pick up the tea kettle from the stove
Turn around walk straight slightly then turn left and walk to the sink and face it
Place the tea kettle in the sink rinse and remove it from the sink
Turn right walk straight slightly then turn right and walk to the white kitchen table and face it
Place the tea kettle on the white table
anns.task_desc: Rinse a tea kettle and place it on the kitchen table

high_descs: Go to the stove ahead of you.
Pick up the kettle from the stove.
Turn around and move forward, then turn left to go to the sink.
Clean the kettle in the sink.
Turn right and go toward the door, then turn right and go towards the wall, then turn right to face the white table.
Put the kettle on the white table.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean kettle on the white table.
